Nine members of a church are nursing injuries after they were attacked during a prayer session in Matungu constituency, Kakamega County. The Wednesday night incident at Eshimuli village saw faithful of the Matungu Baptist Church attacked by assailants armed with crude weapons. ALSO READ:

